name: Trap-Jaw Cyberse Beetle
text:
2 Insect Effect monsters
If an Insect monster is Special Summoned to a Zone this card points to: You can activate one of these effects:●Fusion: Draw 1 card.●Synchro: Special Summon 1 Level 2 or lower Insect monster from your hand or GY, but banish it when it leaves the field.●Xyz: Add 1 "Trap-Jaw" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand.
